# Linting / Formatting

This repo uses **Biome**, not ESLint or Prettier.

- Do NOT add `// eslint-disable-next-line …` or `/* eslint-disable … */` comments anywhere. They are dead code.
- If a Biome rule genuinely needs to be suppressed inline, use `// biome-ignore <rule>: <reason>` with a real justification.
- Do NOT add `// prettier-ignore` either.
- Prefer fixing the underlying issue over suppressing.

Config lives in `biome.json` at the repo root.
